        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 1. Map of Saudi Arabian provinces and distribution of Thorictinae species." , "Figure 14. Barbary fig or cactus pear shrubs, Opuntia ficus-indica (L.) Mill., the type locality of paratype of Thorictus shadensis Hava & Abdel-Dayem, sp. nov. at Shada Al Ala Nature Reserve on the Shada Mountain, Baha Province, southwestern Saudi Arabia, at 1563 m elevation." , "Figure 11. Habitus dorsal aspect of Thorictus shadensis Hava & Abdel-Dayem, sp. nov." , "Figure 13. Acacia thorn woodlands, the type locality of Thorictus shadensis Hava & Abdel-Dayem, sp. nov. holotype at Shada Al Ala Nature Reserve on the Shada Mountain, Baha Province, southwestern Saudi Arabia, at an elevation of 695 m." , "Figure 12. Thorictus shadensis Hava & Abdel-Dayem, sp. nov. a head lateral eye b ventral setation on pronotum and metepisternum, T abyssinicus John, 1963 c head lateral eye d ventral setation on pronotum and metepisternum, T dilatipennis Reitter, 1881 e head lateral eye (according to John 1963) f ventral setation on pronotum and metepisternum (according to John 1963)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/529731" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/529728" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/529729" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/529719" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/529730" .

